Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:08.46,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:11.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:15.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:19.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:23.55,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:26.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:31.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:34.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:37.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:41.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:45.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:49.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:55.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:59.49,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:04.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:47.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:51.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:54.92,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}随心所欲地去描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:59.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描绘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:08.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}万里无云的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:11.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无边无际的蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:15.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}纯洁无瑕的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:19.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈着无限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:23.55,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终于能自由翱翔于天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:26.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}长出了美丽的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:31.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无瑕的瞳孔在寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:34.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:37.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那无数的愿望中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:41.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一个能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:45.08,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不愿让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.15,0:01:49.08,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要紧紧抓住那梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:55.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:59.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描写
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:04.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈愿的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…兄长…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 大神一直与我们同在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是为了抵达这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而事先注定好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是被引导的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传颂之物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为有你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非也 吾等才是灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 吾等才是灾祸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等才是元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 空蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等的力量远不止于此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑制不住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这份冲动 如何抑制得住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻 眼前有吾 有汝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.05,0:03:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是虚无的存在才相互憎恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等一直相恨着 引导着人们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方究竟有何物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安逸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安逸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾的子孙 到达吾的高度之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能从无限孤独中得到解放
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因为这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想不起来么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得很香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她总是睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.74,0:04:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点也和你一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有总是睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲给的珍贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿这孩子永远幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的孩子还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了 ICEMAN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 你面具的复制品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 实在太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把这带上 力量就不断涌现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代谢功能 免疫力 都不是以往所能相提并论的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一来我们人类再次回到地上的日子也不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指的是那个实验体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是第一个成为母体的珍贵样本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解体后慎重地保管了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解体！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢那种的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你再制造10个 20个都无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么 你那么想要强大的肉体么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么想要不死之身么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个愿望 就帮汝实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来永劫 不死之身现在就给汝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来阻止我 阻止我 快阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果阻止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把吾毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 你终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的愿望就是我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 睦美也未能毁灭吾等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可奈何下 睦美将吾等封印在了此地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 在封印前分离的两颗心始终没有合一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等就这样进入了长眠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 之后吾等重复着沉睡与觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并干涉吾等的子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了引导吾等的子孙向上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因你这样照看孩子而给人们带来苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等会引导人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 吾等是多余的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人会凭着自己的意志生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你欲再次与我合二为一吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 吾的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 如你所见 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但哈克奥罗还是哈克奥罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还愿意这么喊我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好听话的 所以 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个样子 已经无法再抚摸你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 骗人 骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过要一直在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 爸爸不一直在一起的话不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将吾封印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在犹豫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以人的身份 封印解放者…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来一起承担
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小神结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然父亲选择长眠 那我就只有服从
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 把这孩子还你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神结
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神结
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 乌露特莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶在另一个我暴动之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若吾等被大神庇佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若吾等背负着大罪 命运被注定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻 再次打开牢狱之门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把吾等的父亲 召唤至常世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快动手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌露特莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后 纷争应该还会持续
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 希望你为此奔波 进行调解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 谨记托付
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神结 还是 睦美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是神结
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睦美也应该很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔不要忘了神结啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这次绝不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调皮而怕寂寞的可爱的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来你是不该受任何束缚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后 就自由自在地生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:14:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 这用不着说 我一直以来活得都自由自在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而今后 我还是主人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下也要永远伴随您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东霞 你已尽忠了 感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下受之有愧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也应该会战乱不断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而牺牲者 则是不拥有力量的弱者们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就成为那些人的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那位源次丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 牺牲性命也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝纳威
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.05,0:14:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙你们照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的事交给我们 请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家都拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣上当初救了我 使我能够履行职责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.93,0:14:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为武士 实感万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总大将 别说客套话了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是 克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也拜托你协助大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 总大将之命 我受领了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧 之后的事都交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后由你来引领大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发过誓要永远与兄长同在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.39,0:15:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人 我们也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.70,0:15:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多利 古拉 胧拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧 你可不能丢下柚叶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 后事就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 阿露露也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连阿露露都不在了 艾露露该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下来的人该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:16:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露有艾露露 有朋友 有许多兄弟姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗 要走了对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 暂时 我要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的事 请交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗不用担心任何事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时 暂时大约是多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过我们是家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过要我们陪伴的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 你的感情 只是刻在契约上的赝品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗并非常人的事 因此而痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切 我全知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但与这些无关
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗救了阿露露 给了我们温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为大家尽了力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这样的哈克奥罗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想说喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗受伤 痛苦 烦恼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想抱住你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和契约无关 今后我可以抱住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.15,0:17:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种说法 太狡猾了 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然到现在才发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 还能相见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.73,0:18:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2000)}一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 你喜欢的铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样 我走了 柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 暂时交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不够成熟 并非坐御座的料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你们不用再被父母那一代的盟约束缚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来 你们尽忠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能侍奉少主 还不如掉入地狱最底层
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您 请让我们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 就随我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只因为无聊 就要把同伴作为雇佣兵出卖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没有出卖你 又没拿到钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这瓶酒又是在哪得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这在世间就叫做出卖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣上 在下还远不够成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点 不好好跑会有麻烦的 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤大僧正
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下又留下这东西跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿这孩子没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不能一笑了之啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 那孩子已经学会重要的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.42,0:20:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库娅大人 差不多到午睡时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被蛰了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿蜂巢很难
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越难越好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然小阿露这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午好 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露大人 中午好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿的情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 多亏你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一来又能和鬼媳妇作战了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请适可而止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 已经能起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经在帮妈妈的忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.44,0:22:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露大人 不知该如何感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我只是轻轻推了一把
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子是靠自己好起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露大人 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷的腰又散架了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又这样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点 请快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奥罗 我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿露露一起 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2000)}永远在这里 等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:37.40,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}きみの瞳に映る　わたしは何色ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:53.19,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}赤深き望むなら　渡そう陽の光を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:26.97,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}悲しみが溢れ　瞼閉じました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:39.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれた滴は　心に沁みゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:50.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}行き渡る波は　弱く交えます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:18:02.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とどけしゆりかご　眠りをさそう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:15.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夢になつかし　面影をさがす
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:28.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を伸ばし　強く　抱きしめたくなる
